Global Energy Recovery Ventilator Market Insights
Energy Recovery Ventilator Market size was valued at USD 3.12 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.67 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Energy Recovery Ventilator Market Overview
The global energy recovery ventilator (ERV) market size was valued at USD 3.58 billion in 2023 and is expected to expand at a CAGR of 8.4% from 2024 to 2030. The increasing demand for energy-efficient ventilation systems, especially in residential and commercial buildings, is driving market growth. Government regulations aimed at reducing energy consumption and promoting sustainable construction practices are expected to further fuel market expansion. As a result, ERVs are gaining popularity for improving indoor air quality, reducing energy costs, and enhancing overall building performance. Key players are focusing on technological advancements and product innovation to cater to the growing market demand.

